{"tid":648884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[鬼?]勁驚嚇！港大站驚現人臉牆","createTime":"2018-05-01T06:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T15:33:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"22e187aa77f5ac62b1ef9e558a57593c98c6e470","tid":648884,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:09:35.000Z","msg":"香港大學站驚現「人臉牆」，嚇煞途人！近日有網民發現，有疑似「人臉」的詭異圖案，浮現於港鐵香港大學站內的牆壁上，不禁令網民驚呼︰「真係咁猛」？<br />\n<br />\n貼文於上周六（28日）被發布至社交群組「西環變幻時」，從片段可見，於鋼門對上的牆壁位置，有一處深色的污漬。離奇的是，當離遠觀看時，該污漬竟隱約透出一個疑似男性的人形臉孔。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民紛指「恐怖」、「有鬼」，亦有人置之一笑，笑言「鬼臉」的樣子「有啲似佛地魔同蒙羅麗莎」。另有網民指早已發現「人臉牆」的存在，「我上星期搭扶手電梯落去時已經見到，我以為得我一個覺得似添」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180501/bkn-20180501115841323-0501_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180501%2Fbkn-20180501115841323-0501_00822_001.html&d=UfzwEr7swUaU76yTx326%2FAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a48e65b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180501/bkn-20180501115841323-0501_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1577599ba1e16913177f39afcce5a158f81f5f73","tid":648884,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180501/photo/bkn-20180501115841323-0501_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180501120636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180501%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180501115841323-0501_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180501120636&h=800daa03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b638865201e9d9c19e24a9f74f44f427f21a141c","tid":648884,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c709c758e5f416ea8d13f4a3eb98649296809c","tid":648884,"uid":19454,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://im